{"tid":992692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女扮男裝混入男同志圈騙錢　睡一個月沒人發現","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T12:41:56.000Z","uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78b0b9e41c49c79b69f7746ffaa1c98f2daebb02","tid":992692,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_afb43ed80614aea9bd6349656b3ffd03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_afb43ed80614aea9bd6349656b3ffd03.jpg&h=1f9177fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國一名作家「王泡小泡」在《微博》發文指出，聽說在深圳有一個Tomboy（簡稱T），假裝成男的，跟男同志談戀愛，騙吃騙喝騙錢，騙了不少人，還有一位男同志跟她睡了一個月，沒發現她是女的。並且分享爆料人提供的照片，並說「她是女的，偽裝功力太強以至於所有知道真相的我們都驚呆了，長年偽裝成男同志在各大同志圈拉拉圈騙錢，你身邊一定有受害者認識她」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n網友看到後紛紛留言「睡一起看不出來摸不出來嗎?」、「這..真看不出來」、「看喉結看不出來嗎?」、「一般人還真的看不出來」、「我猜是跨性別的」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fae471c6e040eefe616750aeabd88ed9b9e6fd6","tid":992692,"uid":34456,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"一個tomboy扮基追男仔<br />\n咁佢係gay定les<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb4d4a866e030aa90ab1e641a11beba0b121ee0","tid":992692,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"就咁睇樣真係呃到好多人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7d6eda58dafbdf2e214b985106e71ed017e833","tid":992692,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"有鬚根喎<br />\n條仔比人屈係女就真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279e538d728b828999fb41366876e95e600e57d5","tid":992692,"uid":30285,